'''''Agence Nationale de l'Aviation Civil''''' is the [[civil aviation]] agency of [[Gabon]]. Its head office is in [[Libreville]].<ref>"[http://www.anac.ga/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=119&Itemid=29 Mentions légales] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110124111339/http://www.anac.ga/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=119&Itemid=29 |date=January 24, 2011 }}." Agence Nationale de l'Aviation Civil. Retrieved on 6 February 2011. AGENCE NATIONALE DE L'AVIATION CIVILE (ANAC) BP 2212 Libreville / Gabon"</ref>

The predecessor agency, the ''Secrétariat Général à l'Aviation Civile et Commerciale'' (SGACC), was established in 1972. The current ANAC was established according to law 005/2008 of 11 July 2008.<ref>"[http://www.anacgabon.org/fr/index.php/a-propos-de-lanac Tout savoir sur l'Agence Nationale de l'Aviation Civile]." ([https://www.webcitation.org/6Gk59ofY1?url=http://www.anacgabon.org/fr/index.php/a-propos-de-lanac Archive]) ''Agence Nationale de l'Aviation Civil''. Retrieved on 19 May 2013.</ref>

