{{redirect|Russian time|the auto racing team known as Russian Time|Motopark Academy}} {{Time zones of Russia}} {{Use dmy dates|date=August 2013}}<!--[[WP:STRONGNAT]]--> There are eleven '''[[time zone]]s in [[Russia]]''', which currently observe times ranging from [[UTC+02:00]] to [[UTC+12:00]]. [[Daylight saving time]] is not used in Russia (since March 2011). __TOC__ {{clear}}
